    <text id="F0904T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>McElheney scolds his wife for not writing more often. He also writes about
                    applying for a furlough and making rings out of rebel shells.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>
        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <opener>
                    <name type="recipient">Harriet McElheney</name>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1865-03-01">March the 1st, 1865</date>
                        <name type="place">Camp in Front of Petersburg</name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>Dear Wife</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>It is with <orig reg="pleasure">pleser</orig> that I take the <orig
                        reg="opportunity">oppertunity</orig> to let you <orig reg="know">now</orig>
                    that I am well at present and hope <orig reg="these">theas</orig>
                    <orig reg="few  
 lines">feulines</orig>
                    <orig reg="will">wil</orig> find you <orig reg="all">awl</orig>
                    <orig reg="well">wel</orig> but I am <orig reg="beginning">begining</orig> to
                    think that you <orig reg="don't">dont</orig>
                    <orig reg="care">cair</orig>
                    <orig reg="anything">eney thing</orig> About me for if you did you <orig
                        reg="would">wod</orig>
                    <orig reg="attend">ten</orig> to <orig reg="writing">riting</orig> a <orig
                        reg="little">litle</orig> better <orig reg="than">then</orig> you <orig
                        reg="do">dou</orig>. if you <orig reg="would">wod</orig>
                    <orig reg="write">rite</orig>
                    <orig reg="every">evry</orig>
                    <orig reg="week">weak</orig> I <orig reg="would">wod</orig>
                    <orig reg="too">to</orig> but I think if you <orig reg="don't">dont</orig> think
                        <orig reg="worthwhile">werthwile</orig>
                    <orig reg="writing">riting</orig> I <orig reg="won't">wont</orig>
                    <orig reg="either">ether</orig>. I <orig reg="haven't">hevent</orig>
                    <orig reg="had">hed</orig> A letter from you for <orig reg="three">thre</orig>
                    <orig reg="weeks">weks</orig>
                    <orig reg="or">er</orig> more. I sent A letter with <unclear><orig reg="Bill"
                            >bil</orig> Sibert</unclear> and I sent <orig reg="three">thre</orig>
                    shirts and a revolver and a pair of <orig reg="gloves">gluves</orig> and a
                        <unclear>testamont</unclear> and a ring and my watch to <orig reg="get it"
                        >getit</orig>
                    <orig reg="fixed">fics</orig>. I told him to fetch the watch<pb n="2"/> back
                    along and I <orig reg="want">won</orig> to <orig reg="know">now</orig> if he
                        <orig reg="gave">giv</orig> you them <orig reg="things">thins</orig>
                    <orig reg="or">er</orig>
                    <orig reg="not">no</orig>. <orig reg="Our">owr</orig>
                    <orig reg="furlough">ferlow</orig> is <orig reg="sent  
 off">sentof</orig> and
                    if it <orig reg="comes">coms</orig>
                    <orig reg="back">bak</orig>
                    <orig reg="all">awl</orig> right we <orig reg="will">wel</orig> get home. we got
                    paid <orig reg="off">of</orig> on <orig reg="Saturday">Satterday</orig> and if
                    we <orig reg="don't">dont</orig> get going home I <orig reg="will">wil</orig>
                    send it home to you and I <orig reg="want">wont</orig> you if <unclear>Kirk</unclear>
                    <orig reg="hasn't">hesent</orig> paid that money to <orig reg="write"
                    >rite</orig> to him that you <orig reg="want it">wontit</orig> as soon as he
                        <orig reg="can">kin</orig>
                    <orig reg="pay it">pait</orig> for I think it is time. I am going to send you
                    and <orig reg="Annie">aney</orig> a ring <orig reg="apiece">a peas</orig>. I
                        <orig reg="made">maid</orig> them out the Rebels <orig reg="shells"
                    >shels</orig> that <orig reg="they">tha</orig>
                    <orig reg="throwed">throed</orig> over and that <orig reg="didn't">diden</orig>
                    bust and I took the <orig reg="screws">scroos</orig> out and <orig reg="made"
                        >maid</orig> them rings. <orig reg="Tell">Tel </orig> miney that I <orig
                        reg="will">wil</orig>
                    <orig reg="make">maike</orig> her <orig reg="one">won</orig> as soon as I <orig
                        reg="can">kin</orig> get a <orig reg="screw">scroo</orig>. So nothing more
                    at present but remain yours. <orig reg="Write">rite</orig> A little sooner <orig
                        reg="than">then</orig> you <unclear>generally</unclear>
                    <orig reg="do">doo</orig>.</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute/>
                    <signed>Sylvester McElheney</signed>
                    <seg type="postscript">If I <orig reg="don't">dont</orig> get <orig reg="going"
                            >goin</orig> home I <orig reg="will">wil</orig> get some <orig
                            reg="photographs">fortgraph</orig> and send them to you I <orig
                            reg="would">wod</orig> like to <orig reg="have">hev</orig> yours.</seg>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
